i N, et al. Intraductal papillary neoplasm of the bile duct: a biliary equivalent to intraductal papillary mucinous neoplasm of the pancreas? <em>Hepatology</em> 2012;56(4):1352–1360.</div><div class="external-links"><div class="core-xlink-crossref"><a href="https://doi.org/10.1002/hep.25786">Crossref</a></div><div class="core-xlink-pubmed"><a href="https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/22504729/">PubMed</a></div><div class="core-xlink-google-scholar"><a href="https://scholar.google.com/scholar_lookup?title=Intraductal+papillary+neoplasm+of+the+bile+duct%3A+a+biliary+equivalent+to+intraductal+papillary+mucinous+neoplasm+of+the+pancreas%3F&amp;author=FG+Rocha&amp;author=H+Lee&amp;author=N+Katabi&amp;publication_year=2012&amp;journal=Hepatology&amp;pages=1352-1360&amp;doi=10.1002%2Fhep.25786&amp;pmid=22504729">Google Scholar</a></div></div></div></div></div><div role="listitem" data-has="label"><div class="label">102.</div><div id="r102" class="citations"><div class="citation"><div class="citation-content">Lim JH, Yoon KH, Kim SH, et al. Intraductal papillary mucinous tumor of the bile ducts. <em>RadioGraphics</em> 2004;24(1):53–66; discussion 66–67.</div><div class="external-links"><div class="core-xlink-crossref"><a href="https://doi.org/10.1148/rg.241035002">Crossref</a></div><div class="core-xlink-pubmed"><a href="https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/14730036/">PubMed</a></div><div class="core-xlink-google-scholar"><a href="https://scholar.google.com/scholar_lookup?title=Intraductal+papillary+mucinous+tumor+of+the+bile+ducts&amp;author=JH+Lim&amp;author=KH+Yoon&amp;author=SH+Kim&amp;publication_year=2004&amp;journal=RadioGraphics&amp;pages=53-66&amp;doi=10.1148%2Frg.241035002&amp;pmid=14730036">Google Scholar</a></div></div></div></div></div><div role="listitem" data-has="label"><div class="label">103.</div><div id="r103" class="citations"><div class="citation"><div class="citation-content">Yeh TS, Tseng JH, Chen TC, et al. Characterization of intrahepatic cholangiocarcinoma